al" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>10/9/00</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>7:46:13 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Iskandar's right</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">It's not about the sentimentality, it's about learning how to be a &lt;insert class here&gt; on a big raid.<br>
<br>
Certainly there's not a LOT to learn, and I think any normal person can learn how to go on big raids effectively after only a few successful raids.  Toss in a failed raid or two and you have yourself an experienced raider, who knows both what to do and what not to do. <br>
<br>
But if people don't learn how to work in multi-group situations, what happens when they go to the planes or a dragon raid the first time?  If they aren't so hot at following directions (which accounts for what, 75% of the populace?) they may do something that endangers the lives of other raiders, experienced or not.<br>
<br>
Anyone who is at the level 40-45 range needs to take it upon themselves to get involved on some of the multi-group raids appropriate to that level, which includes fire giants.  It introduces the concept of multi-group raiding (with its benefits, flaws, and quirks), multi-group looting procedures (with its benefits, flaws, and quirks), multi-group corpse recovery (with its blah blah), and the raid calendar.  <br>
<br>
All in all, a very valuable experience for anyone looking to go to Hate, Fear, Naggy, Vox, and later on, Sky, the new dragons, Trakanon, and so on, whether as a raider, or a raid leader.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#DDDDAA><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uiskandar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Iskandar</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>10/9/00</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>9:08:03 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><img src=http://www.thegamevine.com/~Spoony_Bard/knight1.jpg width=113 height=107></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Iskandar's right</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Haha Cisne. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> </font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=95%><TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT></TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fprexus95980general.showMessage?topicID=4640.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1><< Prev Topic</FONT></A> &nbsp;<A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fprexus95980general.showMessage?topicID=4655.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Next Topic >></FONT></A> </TD></TR></TABLE><BR><TABLE WIDTH=95% BORDER=0><TR><TD><A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fprexus95980general.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4551.topic&index=34><IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0></A></TD><TD><A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fprexus95980general.emailToFriend?topicID=4551.topic><IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/images/email.gif BORDER=0 ALT="Email This To a Friend"></A><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>&nbsp;Email This To a Friend</FONT><BR><A HREF=http://p